      .title.text-center
        span Deep Winter Development

      .down-arrow.text-center
        img(src="images/arrow.svg")
    .services
      .container
        .row.text-center
          h2 SERVICES
        .service-icons
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/idea.svg")
            h3 BRAINSTORM
            p 
              | We discuss your idea for free.
              | Our goal is to understand not just what you want but also why.
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/design2.svg")
            h3 DESIGN
            p
              | We use sketches and moch-ups to find the perfect form to your taste without sacrificing function.
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/develop.svg")
            h3 DEVELOP
            p
              | Fluent in a variety of technologies, our engineers use
              | the right tool for the job to deliver the best product in the least amount of time.
      .container
        .row.text-center
          h2 FEATURES
        .service-icons
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/responsive.svg")
            h3 RESPONSIVE
            p
              | Our mobile first philosophy ensures that your site will look great on any device.
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/fast.svg")
            h3 FAST
            p
              | Compression and asynchronous asset loading makes our sites fly.
          .col-md-4
            img(src="images/secure.svg")
            h3 SECURE
            p
              | Attention to security and thourough penetration testing mean your data stays safe and secure.

